Author: Alright#0419
Content:
3 open positions for LABS notaries are up for grabs right now. Running a LABS NN is a great way to get started with blockchain development, basically forces you to learn. To get a spot, you must enter(and win) a provably fair "lottery". Deadline to enter is Oct 27 (1572202066). Inquire in #kmdlabs if you're interested. No cost to enter, just show you're competent or at least willing to learn.

edit: to be clear, this is for LABS notary positions, not KMD

Author: mrlynch#5735
Content:
:pirate:  Saturday November 9th 1pm-3pm EST (GMT -5) :pirate:  
:realpirate: Cayman Islands Pirates Week Festival -Privacy Conference & Live Stream Info :realpirate: 

`Join us as we discuss the current state of privacy, cryptocurrency and YOU!`  

`We are hosting this event in theater one,at the Camana Bay Cinema in the Cayman Islands. 55 Market Street, Grand Cayman, KY KY11003` 

`The event itself is free to attend for anyone who can make it and for everyone else worldwide you can enjoy our live stream of the event`

`We will be streaming the conference live from 1pm-3pm EST on all possible social media outlets, links and additional details to follow.` 

`There will be an introduction by First mate Lootz, the main presentation by Captain Draeth followed by a Q&A session.`

`Attendees will have the choice of either a commemorative coin or coin key chain.`

The Facebook event page is also now live for the festival and conference live stream event! The presentation is geared towards no-coiners/noobs/normies, so please, if you use FB invite those that you thing should watch the stream! 

https://www.facebook.com/events/530033311119615/
